name: MAXGENEROUSITY
description:
My contribution to #objkt4objkt 09/09 

This is the tribe's first tribute, dedicated to none other than Mr @MAXCAPACITY, the originator of the worldwide objkt4objkt craze of 2021!
The recognisable characteristics of Max's work are incorporated in this piece giving the viewer a feel of an almost... collaborative nature.
 
999 editions will be minted and collectable until the end of the month when all remaining copies will be burned.
If you do collect multiple editions please consider sending them to friends as a gift 🙏🏽💚 


👁️
